Coffee and light snacks will be served.

## When:

-    August 30
-    September 6
-    September 13

## Time:

-    10:00 am – 2:00 pm (drop in anytime)

## Location:

[Jimmy’s Coffee (3 rd floor) - 84 Gerrard Street West](https://www.google.ca/maps/place/Jimmy's+Coffee/@43.658447,-79.3855561,15z/data=!4m5!3m4!1s0x0:0x58d5f2368e2c7a85!8m2!3d43.658447!4d-79.3855561)
(north side of Gerrard between Elizabeth and Bay)

## Ask us…

Do you have questions?

-    what is a union and what do unions do?
-    why did the employer send me a letter about unionization?
-    what are my rights in the workplace?
-    how can I get involved?

Lean more about the UHN union drives at: [cupehospitals.ca/uhn]
